%%Asset Lifecycle Flow
graph TD
    subgraph Planning
        P1[Need Assessment] --> P2[Budget Allocation]
        P2 --> P3[Procurement Plan]
    end

    subgraph Acquisition
        P3 --> A1[Vendor Selection]
        A1 --> A2[Purchase]
        A2 --> A3[Asset Reception]
    end

    subgraph Operation
        A3 --> O1[Deployment]
        O1 --> O2[Maintenance]
        O2 --> O3[Performance Monitoring]
    end

    subgraph Retirement
        O3 --> R1[End-of-Life Assessment]
        R1 --> R2[Decommissioning]
        R2 --> R3[Disposal]
    end